<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">++++</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">삼킴 장애 (dysphagia)</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">+</span></td>
</tr>','<tr>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">++++</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">목 이물감 (globus sensation)</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">+</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">+</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">가슴쓰림 (heartburn sensation)</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">++++</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">+</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;"> 트림, 역류 (reflux symptom)</span></td>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">++++</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-size: 16px;">+++</span></td>
