<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: justify;"><a href="https://blog.naver.com/dizzy_master"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 8px;"><img src="https://img.pilly.kr/story/202207/20220704/1fd416d9-4872-4712-b10c-8603f79bd034.png" alt="" width="1500" height="420"></span></span></span></a></p>
<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>입술</strong>은 <strong>외상</strong>으로<strong> 상처</strong>가 나기도 하지만<br><strong>스트레스</strong>로 <strong>물집</strong>이 생기기도 하므로<br><span style="color: rgb(224, 62, 45);">면역력 강화에 힘써야 합니다</span><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;">3분 건강 체크로</span><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;">여러분에게 꼭 필요한 영양소&nbsp;</span><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;">필리가 알려 드립니다</span><br><br></span><br><br><a href="/survey" class="gtag" gtag-action="btn_click" gtag-category="story_content" gtag-content="content_lips-scratch"> <img src="https://img.pilly.kr/story/202208/20220805/7f700c1c-a5f8-4f0e-98b7-7e736b31f47d.png" alt="" width="1500" height="271"></a></p>
